title: Top legislator meets Georgian parliament's speaker (Beijing Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Beijing Municipal Government ) Zhang Dejiang (R), chairman of the National People's Congress ( NPC) Standing Committee , meets with Speaker of the Parliament of Georgia Davit Usupashvili in Beijing, capital of China , Oct. 14 , 2015 .
